          <td class="cra-layer">Frontend</td>
          <td class="cra-tech">Razor Views, jQuery 3.x, DataTables 1.10, Kendo UI, Knockout.js 3.5, Bootstrap 3, SweetAlert2, select2, moment.js</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="cra-layer">Web Framework</td>
          <td class="cra-tech">ASP.NET MVC 5.2, SimpleInjector 5.0, AutoMapper 7.0</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="cra-layer">Data Access</td>
          <td class="cra-tech">Entity Framework 6.4 (Database-First), Generic Repository + Unit of Work</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="cra-layer">Database</td>
          <td class="cra-tech">SQL Server (90+ tables, views, stored procedures, Power BI views)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="cra-layer">Batch Processing</td>
          <td class="cra-tech">Quartz.NET 2.6, Windows Services (x2: batch + scheduler), 23 EDI executors</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="cra-layer">Reporting</td>
          <td class="cra-tech">EPPlus 5.5, SpreadsheetLight, SSRS via ReportViewer, Power BI pre-calc views</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="cra-layer">SAP Integration</td>
          <td class="cra-tech">XML/EDI file pickup, MB51, FBL1N, FBL3N, FB03, VLO60, CK5, ZAAP_SALES</td>
        </tr>
